# Pre-commit (FAST gate — runs on every commit, <10s budget):
#   1. lint-staged   — ESLint on staged files (autofix + max-warnings=0)
#   2. i18n:check    — locale parity + char limits + types regen (~3s)
#
# tsc + tests + full lint live in pre-push (slower, run less often) to keep
# the inner-loop responsive. CI re-runs everything on push.
#
# If a commit fails because of i18n:check, run `npm run i18n:gen` and stage
# the regenerated keys.generated.ts. If lint-staged fails, fix the file(s)
# it points at.
npx lint-staged
npm run i18n:check
